metadata.name: VAPORWAVE_IS_DEAD_1
metadata.description:
Vaporwave is a hyper-specific subgenre, or "microgenre," that is both a form of electronic music and an art style, although it is sometimes suggested to be primarily a visual medium. Statues represent the re-appropriation of classical art into popular culture, the 80s/90s in particular seemed to have a obsession with revitalizing classic designs to appear "modern", which now appear kitschy and dated.

Size: 4000px x 4000px  
Format: JPG  
3D Render: C4D, Redshift, After Effects
